the confidence to execute plan B.

319
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:36,277
And you have given me
a delightful snack.

320
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:39,989
I love this new era. We should have
gotten divorced years ago.

321
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:41,909
Thank you, Jimmy.

322
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:58,151
Hey, there she is.

323
00:17:58,600 --> 00:18:02,434
