332
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:36,588
Look, right there.
That's a good-looking human being.

333
00:18:36,760 --> 00:18:38,910
-He is cute.
-I told you.

334
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:41,355
But here's the thing, though.
Is he cuter than me?

335
00:18:41,520 --> 00:18:44,034
Should I not have him sit
at the same table as my date?

336
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,519
You're cute too.

337
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:49,673
Really? But cuter than Ryan? I mean,
I just don't want him overwhelming me.

338
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:52,195
I don't think that's possible.

339
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:54,914
You think I'm cute.

340
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:57,469
