-Hey.

341
00:18:57,880 --> 00:19:00,838
Ryan, Alex. Alex, Ryan.

342
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:04,031
Lindsay, Seth. Seth, Lindsay.

343
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:05,918
How could I forget?

344
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:17,871
Well, this should be great.
Really great. And not at all awkward.

345
00:19:23,280 --> 00:19:25,669
