the complete runaround.

354
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:54,069
T oday he sent me to go meet
with his former assistant Phyllis.

355
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:56,276
-Phyllis died last year.
-Exactly.

356
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:58,510
Literally, dead ends.

357
00:19:58,680 --> 00:20:00,796
That's the best lead he's given me yet.

358
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:04,794
Julie seems to be on the same
seek-and-destroy mission as my dad.

359
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:07,429
