360
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:11,030
-...I might as well--
-Give up. Why don't we give up?

361
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:12,958
Give up with me, honey.

362
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:15,793
We could let the gruesome
twosome destroy our careers...

363
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:19,111
...or we could sit here and enjoy
obscene amounts of Dr. Phil...

364
00:20:19,280 --> 00:20:22,272
-...and destroy them ourselves.
-Sandy.

365
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:26,514
If my dad is acting all weird,
he's hiding something.

366
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:29,033
I know.

367
00:20:29,320 --> 00:20:33,074
Which means it's your job
to figure out what that is.

368
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:46,757
I'm not your favorite person right now,
but I can make it up to you.

369
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:49,150
