-Let's have a party.

370
00:20:49,600 --> 00:20:51,716
Sure. Julie, can we talk
about this tomorrow?

371
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:54,917
Sure, we can. Unfortunately,
the caterers are here right now.

372
00:20:55,080 --> 00:20:57,071
Come on in, guys. This way.

373
00:20:57,240 --> 00:20:59,435
-What's going on?
-You know, here's the thing.

374
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:02,068
I knew if I asked in advance,
you'd probably say no.

375
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:06,553
So I called Mr. Herbert and several other
clients and invited them to a party.

376
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,358
-At our house?
-T onight?

377
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:11,474
