389
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:41,237
-Dude, I'm dying here.
-My guess is the secret conference...

390
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:44,119
-...isn't helping.
-The good news is we hit rock bottom.

391
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:47,272
