Riverside to become head Newpsie.

429
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:14,836
Then landed Newport's biggest tycoon
and took over his company.

430
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:17,276
She knows what she's doing.

431
00:25:28,320 --> 00:25:31,995
